<body>

    <h1>UPNP</h1>

        <p>Interface to monitor UPNP devices.</p>

    <h2>Description</h2>
        <p>This event handler searches for and monitors UPNP devices, primarily Audio and Video devices.</p>

    <h2>Configuration</h2>
        <p>This event handler has the following parameters:</p>
        <ul>
        <li>webserver section - attributes serverport and interface, these can both be left blank or zero.</li>
        <li>includedevice section - A list of modelName strings that if found in a retrieved device modelName
	    forces the device to be visible.</li>
        <li>excludedevice section - A list of modelName strings that if found in a retrieved device modelName
	    forces the device to be invisible, note include overrides exclude.</li>
        </ul>
        
    <h2>Events</h2>
        <p>The interface generates av events http://id.webbrick.co.uk/events/av/index.html</p>

    <h2>Example</h2>
